{ White prevents any ...Bc4 ideas and hopes to get his knight to c5 via e4. }
12... Nb4 { Simple and good. Black threatens ...Nca4 is another idea. } 13. Rd1
c6
{ Black's usual two-step manoeuvre of ...Nb4 + ...c6 has been completed. White's bishop is blunted and black has developed soundly. Black has a comfortable position. }
