12. d6
{ This ambitious move was the choice of Carlsen when faced with this variation as white. It of course needs to be taken seriously, but it seems like black is fine here. }
12... Re8
{ Of course some immediate discovered attacks  (like ...Nd5)  are tempting, but this preparatory move  (threatening ...Nxe4)  is better. }
