7. Be3 O-O 8. Be2 { A natural developing move. } 8... Nc6 9. d5 Ne5 10. Bd4 c5
{ A sacrifice which also occasionally features in the 3. f3 d5 Grunfeld. The bishop is temporarily lured away. }
11. Bxc5 Nec4
{ Black's activity and the possibility of ...Nxb2 followed up by ...Qc7 for example grant him full equality. }
